<L>__{exterior de leesepses' house. night.}
<A>__{male voice shout to each other inside the house, candle flames appear in different windows, the garden door is flung open, revealing sir robert with candelabra in one hand and sword in the other. by this time will is on top of the garden wall and he drops safely out of sight. he could have written it better.}
<L>__{interior will's room. dawn.}
<A>__{will is burning the midnight oil literally and metaphorically. his quill has already covered a dozen sheets. he is inspired.}
